translated: Billing, Ernst Ludvig, advertising manager, Gothenburg, born June 20, 1874 in Gothenburg to Anders B. and Antoinetta Vilhelmina Pyk. Married in 1899 to Sofia Nilsson. Children: Allan, born in 1901, bank clerk in Gothenburg, Alva, born in 1902, cashier, Ann-Marie, born in 1909, cashier, Lars Erik, born in 1911, employee, Ann Britt, born in 1914, office clerk. Traveled for H. L. Ygberg in Gothenburg from 1892-1894, worked for Gbgs Nyheter from 1894-1898, advertising manager at Gbgs-Posten since 1898. Member of the Gothenburg and Western Sweden press association, member of the Publishers' Club since 1912, member of the Göta Coldinu Order. Member of Par Bricole, W-Sex, and Temple Knight Order. Hobby: singing.
